{{message box|heading=This Wikibook is being majorly rewritten|message=Due to the new A-level specification it is out of date.  A lot of activity should be happening here now.}}

This Wikibook is about [[w:Advanced Level (UK)|A-level]] Chemistry, designed to follow the OCR (Salters) syllabus, but is not endorsed by [[w:OCR (examination board)|OCR]]. It will hopefully be useful as a revision guide or for alternative explanations to the ones in your textbook or from your tutor.

